{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001915", "chronotag": "1757948802249", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "1915", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1915", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC1364", "triAmendement": "buaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabbmuj", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA840809", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO847173", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Verny"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 6", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 6", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 6", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1364.asp#D_Article_6"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "12", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 12"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00C0;&nbsp;l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;12, substituer au mot&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;quinze&nbsp;&#x00BB;,&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;vingt-cinq&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement vise &#x00E0; porter de quinze &#x00E0; vingt-cinq jours le d&#x00E9;lai laiss&#x00E9; au m&#x00E9;decin pour se prononcer sur une demande d&#x2019;aide m&#x00E9;dicale &#x00E0; mourir, &#x00E0; compter de sa r&#x00E9;ception.</p><p>Ce d&#x00E9;lai allong&#x00E9; a pour objet de garantir une &#x00E9;valuation approfondie, &#x00E9;clair&#x00E9;e et responsable, &#x00E0; la hauteur de la gravit&#x00E9; irr&#x00E9;versible de l&#x2019;acte envisag&#x00E9;. Quinze jours peuvent s&#x2019;av&#x00E9;rer insuffisants pour organiser l&#x2019;ensemble des entretiens m&#x00E9;dicaux, recueillir les avis sp&#x00E9;cialis&#x00E9;s n&#x00E9;cessaires, consulter les proches ou la personne de confiance, et analyser pleinement la situation m&#x00E9;dicale, psychique, sociale et familiale du demandeur.</p><p>En portant ce d&#x00E9;lai &#x00E0; vingt-cinq jours, l&#x2019;amendement permet de pr&#x00E9;server la qualit&#x00E9; du discernement m&#x00E9;dical, d&#x2019;&#x00E9;viter les d&#x00E9;cisions h&#x00E2;tives, et de renforcer les garanties de s&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; et d&#x2019;&#x00E9;quit&#x00E9; proc&#x00E9;durale. Ce d&#x00E9;lai reste compatible avec les situations cliniques complexes, sans compromettre la r&#x00E9;activit&#x00E9; attendue du corps m&#x00E9;dical.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-05-09", "datePublication": "2025-05-20", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "RT", "libelle": "Retir\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "RT", "libelle": "Retir\u00e9 apr\u00e8s publication"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001915?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "1", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}